"Now, let's go outside and see who we can gather for the Hunt!" Hippolyte strode thru the two walls of sheer peacock patterned curtains, and to the door...stepping out on the top of the steps.  She glanced back at her athelfi, and then smiled seeing Velaska.  <br>
She saluted her, "Yasoo Vel... a good day to Hunt for Artemis, you think?"<br>
As she smiled at Velasca, her eyes were caught to someone being led to her large hut.  Hippolyte raised a brow and knew it was the one who has been spying.  She waved to the guards to let her go and to just lead Destiny to the bottom of the steps.  She could see by her dress that Destiny was amazon and smiled, tho watching her curiously.<br>
"Yasoo, athelfi.  I am Hippolyte, Queen of Themiscrya.  May I ask who you are and why you would spy on our village?" Hippolyte voice was warm and not offensive.  She didn't fear this one, but clearly wanted to know who she was. <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>
