&quot;Yasoo Athelfi, come to join the hunt?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uhippolyte.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hippolyte</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Vasilissa</span><br>  Posts: 329<br> <font color=#993300>(5/18/01 5:09:37 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> The hunt and our visitor</span><hr size=1> Hippolyte raised a brow at the guards. &quot;Do nothing....for she is our athelfi,&quot;she turned to smile at Destiny. &quot;We are about to hunt in honour of Artemis, and you are welcome to join us if you like.&quot;<br>
Hippolyte smiled as more joined them to hunt.  <br>
&quot;Amazons, the light of day is soon to follow Apollo's chariot from our Mountains.  All who feel they are ready to join us ....please honour us with your presence.  As soon as the Moon of Artemis rises over the trees,&quot; Hipp pointed to the eastern sky. &quot;We shall enter the Themiscryan woods.  This hunt is in honour of Artemis. For that we will only take one beast or fowl each.  only ONE.  When you take it's life. Your are to be thankful to Artemis for your success.  And then thank the beast or fowl.  Then you are to take a bite of it's flesh..so that it's essence is now apart of you.  It's blessings from Artemis...now yours.  Then bring your gift back to the tribe...and we shall have a great feast in honour of the Goddess of the Hunt!!!&quot;<br>
Hipp smiled as she glanced around.  She knew it would be hard for some to partake of rare flesh.  It had been hard for her for several years when she first came to Themiscrya.  But...she learned..with time. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/umarpeamzn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Marpe Amzn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#993300>(5/18/01 5:40:24 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Hunt</span><hr size=1> She smiled at her amazon sisters and followed the Queen down her steps, keeping close as the visitor was brought forth.  Marpe listened as the others delt with the situation and then grinned as the Queen described the hunt.  This was something Marpe was good at.  The ability to be a sniper and hunter.  And she was very very ready. She raised her arm in a strong fist. &quot;To Artemis!&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showMessageRange?topicID=207.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showMessageRange?topicID=207.topic&start=41&stop=54>3</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showMessage?topicID=163.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showMessage?topicID=210.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.emailToFriend?topicID=207.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href